text: Snehal Pramod Jadhav (born 17 October 1989) is a Maharashtrian cricketer.Playes's Profile She played for Maharashtra and West zone. She has played 1 First-class, 37 List A and 31 Women's Twenty20 matches. She is a right handed wicket-keeper batsmen. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Maharashtra women cricketers Category:West Zone women cricketers Category:Living people
